" Very Magic
" ----------
" " The following line is equivalent to `cnoremap %s/ %s/\v`.
" cnoremap %s/ %smagic/
" cnoremap \>s/ \>smagic/
" nnoremap :g/ :g/\v
" nnoremap :g// :g//
" nnoremap / /\v
" vnoremap / /\v

